data.description: 2,373 Finished square feet of living space. Located near Crowne baseball park in a nice neighborhood is this multi level home. Vaulted ceilings in the kitchen and living room. Attached finished garage with an extra parking apron. The huge family room is in the daylight portion of the lower level a nice gas fireplace for a focal point. In addition to the 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, there is an above ground pool, garden shed and oversized barn like shed. Also in the back yard is a covered deck, patio and patio garden as well as a wood privacy fence that has hidden steel posts and a 15 year warranty,  The interior of this home is in the process of being painted and the nail holes filled. Appliances are newer and in very good condition. 2024-01-06
